(7, 1, '2007-09-13 12:22:44', '2007-09-13 17:22:44', 'Every once in a while, we need to take a break and bustÂ loose on something cheap.\r\n\r\n<img width="180" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1137/1357871169_b338bab593_m.jpg" height="240" style="width: 180px; height: 240px" />\r\n\r\nI chose to do The Blue-Ring Octopus. One of the most deadly creatures on earth aside from spoiled Turkey.\r\n\r\n<img width="375" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1271/1363751526_d54a27661c.jpg" height="500" style="width: 375px; height: 500px" />\r\n\r\nImagine being paralyzed, but being able to hear and see everyone talking about how dead you are.\r\n\r\nAnd you can''t even feel it bite you.', 'Paulkaijupus #1 The Blue-ring', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paulkaijupus-1-the-blue-ring', '', '', '2007-09-13 12:30:45', '2007-09-13 17:30:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=7', 0, 'post', '', 2),
