(17, 1, '2008-05-13 23:15:18', '2008-05-14 04:15:18', 'This is a vinyl version of a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dog%C5%AB">Dogu</a> figure from the Jomon period.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3075/2461538729_8164899686.jpg" height="500" width="375" />\r\n\r\nEver since seeing the movie "Chariots of the Gods" as a child I have always dreamed of owning one.\r\n\r\nLittle would I expect it would be a vinyl version, but I was just as into it!\r\n\r\nI thought the vinyl color was a bit too much like chocolate, so I converted it to more of a grey stone type color.\r\n\r\nCan''t say I regret it! It really brought out the details.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3101/2461922001_db6d760a60_o.jpg" height="500" width="375" />', 'Marmit Jomon Figure', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marmit-jomon-figure', '', '', '2008-05-13 23:15:18', '2008-05-14 04:15:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=17', 0, 'post', '', 2),
