(381, 1, '2010-05-25 20:01:39', '2010-05-26 03:01:39', 'Wow what a year so far. And it''s accelerating like the expanding universe we live within. Good times.\r\n\r\nMy studio here in old SD is really swinging. gearing up plenty of surprises (I like to keep secrets too!) for\r\n\r\nprobably the next 2 years. One thing I''ve discovered is that sculpting pulls the energy and turns the brain to jelly.\r\n\r\nI think I like my jelly brain as long as I can give you cool toys.\r\n\r\nAnother thing is, going from sculpting back to painting is a really rough transition. I usually get the groove back around lunchtime.\r\n\r\nYou start sculpting in the morning, and before you know it it''s time to sleep. Life''s too damn short I tells ya!\r\n\r\nAnyway...\r\n\r\nIf you happen to be in San Diego on May 29th there''s a cool event at <a href="http://gunnzo.com/store/?utm_source=GUNNZO+List&amp;utm_campaign=ee7804c19f-OpenHouseReminder&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;mc_cid=ee7804c19f&amp;mc_eid=a042606164">Gunnzo</a>.\r\n\r\nI will be hanging out, supporting the custom movement (I consider it a movement!), and judging a contest.\r\n\r\nShould be fun! Show up and give Gunnzo some good ol'' toy community support! Chika''s super cool and her shop is really adorable!\r\n\r\nAs far as this weeks wax mashing, here''s a little preview of the three dudes wearing really cheesy tree suits.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-377" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=377"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-377" title="THE TREES" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/THE-TREES-450x324.jpg" alt="" width="450" height="324" /></a>', 'Sculpting and Gunnzo!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '376-revision-4', '', '', '2010-05-25 20:01:39', '2010-05-26 03:01:39', '', 376, 'http://localhost/pk-new/updates/376-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
