(602, 1, '2010-08-24 10:59:01', '2010-08-24 17:59:01', '<strong>Toxic Catalyst!</strong>\r\n\r\nWhile I was not able to attend the AWESOME looking Toxic Catalyst show last weekend at Super7, some folks were there enjoying the gathering.\r\n\r\nThere are a few you can review here:\r\n<a href="http://toybotstudios.blogspot.com/2010/08/toxic-catalyst-show-recap.html#more">Toybot Studios</a>\r\n<a href="http://robotxmonster.blogspot.com/">Robotxmonster</a>\r\n<a href="http://blog.neonmonster.com/gallery/romping-around-with-the-resonators-at-toxic-catalyst/">Neon Monster</a>\r\n\r\nLeft overs are still up at the <a href="http://super7store.com/art.html?p=5">Super 7</a> store!\r\nGreat looking show! Thanks to the artists, MONSTREHERO , Super 7, and all the great folks who attended!\r\nSweet Marrow Mockbat:\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-603" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/toxic-catalyst-and-freemans-sucklord-600-auction/attachment/sweet-marrow-tc/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-603" title="Sweet Marrow TC" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Sweet-Marrow-TC-446x500.jpg" alt="" width="312" height="350" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Freeman''s SUCKLORD 600 Auction!</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Freeman''s Auction House in Philly, the spot that hosted the Vader Project, is offering some of the juciest <em>SUCKLORD 600</em> figures from the <em>SUPER SUCKOFF</em> in their <a href="http://www.freemansauction.com/asp/searchresults.asp?pg=1&amp;ps=25&amp;st=D&amp;sale_no=1377">POP CUTURE</a> sale on September 3rd.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-609" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/toxic-catalyst-and-freemans-sucklord-600-auction/attachment/freemans-cov/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-609" title="Freemans cov" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Freemans-cov-384x500.jpg" alt="" width="384" height="500" /></a>\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">My figure with it''s beautiful header card for the Sucklord 600 will be included in this <a href="http://www.freemansauction.com/asp/fullCatalogue.asp?salelot=1377+++++281+&amp;refno=++747741">auction</a>!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><a rel="attachment wp-att-608" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/toxic-catalyst-and-freemans-sucklord-600-auction/attachment/sucklord/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-608" title="Sucklord" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Sucklord-567x500.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="500" /></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Registration info is <a href="http://www.freemansauction.com/buying.asp">HERE</a>.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Be sure and check out <a href="http://suckadelic.com/Realms2.html">SUCKADELIC</a>!\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">\r\n</span>', 'Toxic Catalyst and Freeman''s SUCKLORD 600 auction!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'toxic-catalyst-and-freemans-sucklord-600-auction', '', '\nhttp://blog.neonmonster.com/gallery/romping-around-with-the-resonators-at-toxic-catalyst/', '2010-08-24 10:59:02', '2010-08-24 17:59:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=602', 0, 'post', '', 0),
