(678, 1, '2010-08-26 21:58:37', '2010-08-27 04:58:37', 'I had been a collector of squeeky toy style elephants for a few years.\n\nIt seems there are so many varieties, sizes, and styles. I am constantly seeing ones I never knew existed.\n\nThis was my main inspiration in making Boss Carrion. He would fit the Elephants and the Kaiju.\n\nHe was cute, gross, and weird.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-662" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=662"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-662" title="The Family" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/The-Family-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="269" /></a>\n\nThe arms, legs, head, and fish all came apart and were held on with wooden pegs so I could test\n\nthe sitting position and movement range.\n\nI didn''t have any sketches, the sculpt rolled out of my mind very smoothly.\n\nHere''s a shot of the original sculpt, still very raw.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-663" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=663"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-663" title="BC2R" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/BC2R-375x500.jpg" alt="" width="375" height="500" /></a>\n\nI had decided while sculpting that some form of creature was needed on his rear.\n\nHe was made of various fused animal parts. I was inspired by a certain Kaiju from a 70''s TV show and decided on a fish.\n\nI had gone through about 3 different tail fish before I settled on the last one.\n\nOne dropped and broke, one got burned, and this one failed my approval.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-664" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=664"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-664" title="Fish" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Fish-374x500.jpg" alt="" width="374" height="500" /></a>\n\nTesting sitting pose.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-677" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=677"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-677" title="Boss Carrion sitting" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Boss-Carrion-sitting-352x500.jpg" alt="" width="352" height="500" /></a>\n\nHere is the final sculpt all surfaced and polished up.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-661" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=661"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-661" title="Boss Carrion Right" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Boss-Carrion-Right-374x500.jpg" alt="" width="374" height="500" /></a>\n\nHere''s a shot of the "Bat Hand" in an earlier sculpt.\n\nI thought it was too flat, but I had a limit because it needed to be able to slip out of the mold during production.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-666" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=666"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-666" title="BC bat hand" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/BC-bat-hand-375x500.jpg" alt="" width="375" height="500" /></a>\n\nImagine the excitement of getting the first test shot in the mail!\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-673" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=673"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-673" title="Boss Carrion test shot" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Boss-Carrion-test-shot-370x500.jpg" alt="" width="370" height="500" /></a>\n\nThen the painted test shot!\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-674" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=674"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-674" title="4x6_postcard_boss" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/4x6_postcard_boss-340x500.jpg" alt="" width="340" height="500" /></a>\n\nPainting the Black and Silver version.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-675" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=675"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-675" title="Black painted" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Black-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>\n\nPainting the Blue version.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-676" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=676"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-676" title="Blue painted" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Blue-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>', 'Boss Carrion: The development', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '659-revision-7', '', '', '2010-08-26 21:58:37', '2010-08-27 04:58:37', '', 659, 'http://localhost/pk-new/blog/659-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
