ze-medium wp-image-677" title="Boss Carrion sitting" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Boss-Carrion-sitting-352x500.jpg" alt="" width="352" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nHere is the final sculpt all surfaced and polished up.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-661" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=661"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-661" title="Boss Carrion Right" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Boss-Carrion-Right-374x500.jpg" alt="" width="374" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nHere''s a shot of the "Bat Hand" in an earlier sculpt.\r\n\r\nI thought it was too flat, but I had a limit because it needed to be able to slip out of the mold during production.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-666" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=666"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-666" title="BC bat hand" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/BC-bat-hand-375x500.jpg" alt="" width="375" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nImagine the excitement of getting the first test shot in the mail!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-673" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=673"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-673" title="Boss Carrion test shot" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Boss-Carrion-test-shot-370x500.jpg" alt="" width="370" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nThen the painted test shot!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-674" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=674"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-674" title="4x6_postcard_boss" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/4x6_postcard_boss-340x500.jpg" alt="" width="340" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nPainting the Black and Silver version.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-675" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=675"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-675" title="Black painted" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Black-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>\r\n\r\nPainting the Blue version.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-676" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=676"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-676" title="Blue painted" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Blue-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>', 'Boss Carrion: The development', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '659-revision-8', '', '', '2010-08-26 21:58:57', '2010-08-27 04:58:57', '', 659, 'http://localhost/pk-new/blog/659-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
