he Blue version.\n\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-676" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=676"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-676" title="Blue painted" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Blue-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>\n\nI''ve developed some tricks for Boss Carrion using magnets. I plan on making strange accesso', 'Boss Carrion: The development', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '659-revision-9', '', '', '2010-08-26 22:02:59', '2010-08-27 05:02:59', '', 659, 'http://localhost/pk-new/blog/659-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
