k-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Black-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>\r\n\r\nPainting the Blue version.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-676" href="http://localhost/pk-new/?attachment_id=676"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-676" title="Blue painted" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Blue-painted-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="449" /></a>\r\n\r\nI''ve developed some tricks for Boss Carrion using magnets and\r\n\r\nplan on making strange accessories to be included with him as a surprise!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-650" href="http://localhost/pk-new/gallery/649/attachment/biter-face/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-650" title="Biter face" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Biter-face-365x500.jpg" alt="" width="365" height="500" /></a>', 'Boss Carrion: The development', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '659-revision-10', '', '', '2010-08-26 22:04:45', '2010-08-27 05:04:45', '', 659, 'http://localhost/pk-new/blog/659-revision-10/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
