(771, 1, '2010-10-22 10:26:45', '2010-10-22 17:26:45', '<a rel="attachment wp-att-772" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/orange-partyball/attachment/partyball_orange_blog/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-772" title="partyball_orange_blog" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/partyball_orange_blog.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nAvailable, Saturday via Super 7, October 30th, $30 each.\r\n\r\nTo quote the Super 7 Blog:\r\n\r\n"The Demon Machine is back from the depths, to rear its gnarly head!  From the monster-warped imagination of Paul Kaiju,\r\n\r\naka the dude who''s  been doing this since before I was born,\r\n\r\ncomes the second painted  release of Partyball,\r\n\r\nsporting colors that would make any vintage  Bullmark melt with envy."\r\n\r\nHey, beauty , knowledge and grace comes with age!', 'Orange Partyball! ', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'orange-partyball', '', '', '2010-10-22 10:26:45', '2010-10-22 17:26:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=771', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(759, 1, '2010-10-14 13:46:25', '2010-10-14 20:46:25', '<strong>ESCAPE FROM NY!</strong>\r\n\r\nI''ve been back from New York for a few days now.\r\n\r\nThe excitement got the best of me and I''m a bit sick.\r\n\r\nBut what a blast I had. Big thanks to the Onell crew for hosting me,\r\n\r\nthe east coast toy community for leading me to the fun,\r\n\r\nand <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/grizlli_atom/">Mr Grizlli Atom</a> for doing these fine prints...\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-763" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/return-from-nycc-and-monstars-at-lower-haters-hachoooo/attachment/grizli-prints/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-763" title="Grizli prints" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/Grizli-prints-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="314" /></a>\r\n\r\nand everyone who showed up and purchased my "special sort of madness".\r\n\r\nI should will have available in my shop along with\r\n\r\nleftovers from NYCC plus more Boss Carrion BUTTERCUP version!\r\n\r\nAs soon as I''m better! I would say in one to two weeks.\r\n\r\n<strong>"MONSTARS" at Lower Haters\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-761" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/return-from-nycc-and-monstars-at-lower-haters-hachoooo/attachment/ms/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-761" title="ms" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/ms.jpg" alt="" width="425" height="638" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-760" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/return-from-nycc-and-monstars-at-lower-haters-hachoooo/attachment/ms-front/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-760" title="MS front" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/MS-front.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="645" /></a>\r\n\r\nHere''s the one off ''Blue" Boss for the show.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-762" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/return-from-nycc-and-monstars-at-lower-haters-hachoooo/attachment/blue-boss-monstars/"><img class="alignnone size-