(792, 1, '2010-11-16 19:51:26', '2010-11-17 02:51:26', 'Hi all,\r\n\r\nTaking a break from the bonds of elf-style self-induced toy slavery and posting to announce\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.designercon.com/">Desingner-con 2010</a>!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-793" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/designercon-2010/attachment/pasedena4/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-793" title="Pasedena4" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Pasedena4-452x500.jpg" alt="" width="586" height="648" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe MONSTREHERO, Uh Oh Toys, John Knox, and I will be there with a booth loaded with a\r\n\r\nbounty of gorgeous hand-forged toy treats! You will be amazed!! Exiting and surreal adventure for the whole family!\r\n\r\nHere''s just a peek of what I will have to offer:\r\n\r\n"Pollen Kaiser" will make his lightly painted debut! Take your antihistamines!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-794" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/designercon-2010/attachment/pollen-kaiser-2/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-794" title="Pollen Kaiser 2" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Pollen-Kaiser-2-374x500.jpg" alt="" width="374" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nBeing a fan of vintage style character related Japanese tin cars I can''t afford, I custom built these "Boss Cars" from Vintage tin, resin, decals, and tears.\r\n\r\nI thought Boss Carrion deserved the "Vintage" treatment.\r\n\r\nThat cute little face riding around and running into other monsters makes me happy I took the plunge into PURE insanity.\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-795" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/designercon-2010/attachment/bosscar/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-795" title="Bosscar" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Bosscar-600x460.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="460" /></a>\r\n\r\nAnd Boss Carrion "Pinkysnouts" are still on the grill...but you know they''ll be ready!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-796" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/designercon-2010/attachment/pinksnouts/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-796" title="Pinksnouts" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Pinksnouts-375x500.jpg" alt="" width="375" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nPlus much. much MORE!\r\n\r\nSee you there!\r\n\r\nPLEASE VISIT DESIGNERCON 2010 WEBSITE FOR MORE INFO!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.designercon.com/">HERE!</a>', 'Designercon 2010!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'designercon-2010', '', '', '2010-11-16 23:21:24', '2010-11-17 06:21:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=792', 0, 'post', '', 1),
