(991, 1, '2011-02-19 10:47:31', '2011-02-19 18:47:31', '<span style="color: #ff99cc;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">PK and LCFR at Super 7</span></span>\r\n\r\nIn a whirlwind attack, Leecifer and I combine forces to give San Francisco one killer show for the end of February!\r\n\r\nAt <a href="http://super7store.com/">Super 7</a> store!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-992" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag/attachment/pk_lcsf_s7_show_eflier/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-992" title="PK_Lcsf_S7_Show_eFlier" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/PK_Lcsf_S7_Show_eFlier-333x500.jpg" alt="" width="333" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nHere''s one preview of what i will be bringing, as well as some vinyl and resin surprises!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-995" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag/attachment/battle-racers/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-995" title="Battle racers" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Battle-racers-387x500.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Boss Racer Vs. Bitemobile-X playset. Resin, Styrene, and <a href="http://monsterkolor.ning.com/">Monster Kolor</a> on vintage tin cars. Limited to ONE</em>\r\n\r\nAlso!\r\n\r\nSome nice exclusives for the show! Including the premier release of Leecifer''s Monster Family member The Flame!\r\n\r\nPartyball in those cool Mecha Godzilla style colors too! Metallic colored Vinyl! Wild! I''ve wanted to see this for some time!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-997" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag/attachment/2_26_release/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-997" title="2_26_release" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/mecha-Partyball.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="387" /></a>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #ff99cc;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Mark Nagata''s Alien Argus group show at TAG</strong></span></span>\r\n\r\nMark Nagata of <a href="http://www.maxtoyco.com/">Maxtoy</a> and <a href="http://www.toyartgallery.com/">Toy Art Gallery</a> are having a group show featuring artists from around the globe taking their spin on Max Toy''s Alien Argus figure!\r\n\r\nThe amount of talent in this show should be one mind warping galactic Pow-wow!\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-993" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag/attachment/argus_postcard_front/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-993" title="ARGUS_POSTCARD_front" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/ARGUS_POSTCARD_front-360x500.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-994" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag/attachment/argus_postcard_back/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-994" title="ARGUS_POSTCARD_back" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/ARGUS_POSTCARD_back-360x500.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nHere''s an image of my entry, "Diane Argus"(Silly name I know, but it stuck!).\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-996" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag/attachment/argus-3/"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-996" title="Argus 3" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Argus-3-349x500.jpg" alt="" width="349" height="500" /></a>', 'Feburary 26th! Two shows! PK and LCFR at Super 7 and Mark Nagata''s Alien Argus group show at TAG!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'feburary-26th-two-shows-pk-and-lcfr-at-super-7-and-mark-nagatas-alien-argus-group-show-at-tag', '', '', '2011-02-19 10:50:15', '2011-02-19 18:50:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=991', 0, 'post', '', 0),
