(1444, 1, '2011-09-10 09:00:23', '2011-09-10 16:00:23', '<p style="text-align: left;">I''ll have 5 one of a kind pieces in this years Toy Karma 3 show.</p>\r\n<a href="http://www.toykarma.rotofugi.com/">Toy Karma 3</a> , curated by Mark Nagata of <a href="http://maxtoyco.com/">Max Toy Company</a> opens tonight at Rotofugi Gallery in Chicago and goes until October 2nd.\r\n\r\nMANY great artists in this show, and some amazing exclusives available this event only!\r\n\r\nAs usual, it''s an honor and a pleasure to take part of what looks like another AMAZING Toy Karma!\r\n\r\nToy Karma is a great reminder that we are all a part of one great monster island, and great toys come in ALL shapes and sizes.\r\n\r\nVariety is a main ingredient vintage recipe of this ever delicious vinyl gravy base we now enjoy, not just some vending machine trend.\r\n\r\nItadakimatsu!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a rel="attachment wp-att-1445" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/toy-karma-3-at-rotofugi/attachment/tk3-amapro/"><img class="size-full wp-image-1445 alignnone" title="tk3-amapro" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/tk3-amapro.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="329" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Saihatari by Amapro</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\r\n</em>\r\n\r\nA preview of 3 one of a kind figures I will have in the show.\r\n\r\n<em>Citrus Boss</em>\r\n\r\n<em><a rel="attachment wp-att-1446" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/toy-karma-3-at-rotofugi/attachment/citrus-boss/"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1446 alignnone" title="CITRUS BOSS" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/CITRUS-BOSS--339x500.jpg" alt="" width="203" height="300" /></a></em>\r\n\r\n<em>"Ape Phase" Salamander Joe</em>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><a rel="attachment wp-att-1447" href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/toy-karma-3-at-rotofugi/attachment/ape-phase/"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1447 alignnone" title="Ape phase" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/Ape-phase-354x500.jpg"