(1793, 1, '2012-07-18 11:20:26', '2012-07-18 18:20:26', 'Thanks to all who attended Super Magic Funtime Unit at <a href="http://www.5andadime.com/">5 &amp; A Dime</a>!\r\n\r\nAwesome coverage can be found at <a href="http://www.vinylpulse.com/2012/07/smfu-event-5a-dime.html#more">Vinyl Pulse</a> !\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/s-m-f-u-thanks-you/attachment/final-smfu/" rel="attachment wp-att-1794"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1794" title="Final SMFU" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/Final-SMFU-600x202.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="202" /></a>\r\n\r\nI would ESPECIALLY like to thank <a href="http://super-junk.com/">Super*Junk</a> for her killer graphics,Â  Kris Funks and Vinyl Pulse,Â  <a href="http://www.5andadime.com/">5 &amp; Dime</a>Â  for hosting us,\r\n\r\nScott HMS, <a href="http://www.lulubelltoys.com/">Lulubell</a> Toy Bodega, Grody Shogun, Velocitron and <a href="http://www.spankystokes.com/">Spankystokes</a> for the nifty coffin.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nMost all vinyls sold out.\r\n\r\nBut I should have some nifty custom leftovers and shirts up in my shop\r\n\r\nas soon as I get rid of this Nerd Flu! Bleh!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'S + M + F + U Thanks you!', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 's-m-f-u-thanks-you', '', '', '2012-07-18 11:20:26', '2012-07-18 18:20:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=1793', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1779, 1, '2012-06-10 10:21:32', '2012-06-10 17:21:32', '<a href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/izakaya-superstars-resuming-the-mission/attachment/the-final-izakaya/" rel="attachment wp-att-1782"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1782" title="The final Izakaya" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/The-final-Izakaya-600x449.jpg" alt="" width="360" height="269" /></a>\r\n\r\nStill waking up thinking I''m in Tokyo after 2 weeks of being back. Post toy mecca shock!\r\n\r\nWhat an amazing trip that was.\r\n\r\nMany new toy deals were forged and special projects to be revealed in the near future!\r\n\r\nGreat time at Designfesta, successful show with Uamou,\r\n\r\nand meeting the LEGENDARY Monster painterÂ  Goto San!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/izakaya-superstars-resuming-the-mission/attachment/goto-bat/" rel="attachment wp-att-1787"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1787" title="Goto Bat" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Goto-Bat--375x500.jpg" alt="" width="263" height="350" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThanks to all who made our visit great! You can check out pics on my <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/paulkaiju/sets/72157629641080834/">Flickr</a>.\r\n\r\nTest shots and the big to do...\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nFIG-LAB FINGER 5\r\n\r\nBeen awhile in the works, but the test shots are here!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/izakaya-superstars-resuming-the-mission/attachment/flff/" rel="attachment wp-att-1780"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1780" title="FLFF" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/FLFF-600x391.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="274" /></a>\r\n\r\nBeen doing test paints on these as well. Super fun to paint for those who are crafty!\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/izakaya-superstars-resuming-the-mission/attachment/sucklord-sd-pheyden-baby-huey-uncle-biter/" rel="attachment wp-att-1788"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-1788" title="Sucklord SD-Pheyden-Baby Huey-Uncle Biter" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Sucklord-SD-Pheyden-Baby-Huey-Uncle-Biter-600x420.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="294" /></a>\r\n\r\nPOLLEN KAISER\r\n\r\nOur favorite resin sinus-annihilator makes his debut in vinyl.\r\n\r\nProduced in association with <a href="http://www.toyartgallery.com/">Toy Art Gallery</a>. This is one beefy dude.\r\n\r\nTest paints are in the works. Introductory vinyl is currently in production.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/pk-new/blog/izakaya-superstars-resuming-the-mission/attachment/monster/" rel="attachment wp-att-1781"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1781" title="Monster" src="http://localhost/pk-new/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/Monster-389x500.jpg" alt="" width="389" height="500" /></a>\r\n\r\nDecided to paint myself one. I suppose there will be many hand paint versions.;)\r\n\r\nSDCC you ask? It''s going to be a little different this year! Stay tuned!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Izakaya superstars! Resuming the mission.', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'izakaya-superstars-resuming-the-mission', '', '', '2012-06-10 10:21:32', '2012-06-10 17:21:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/pk-new/?p=1779', 0, 'post', '', 0),
